- Stan Traub.

230
00:15:24,518 --> 00:15:26,690
Je suis un grand fan
du coach Taylor.

231
00:15:27,882 --> 00:15:28,883
Merci, Stan.

232
00:15:30,347 --> 00:15:32,470
