387
00:24:35,577 --> 00:24:37,206
"Éloigne-toi, Satan..."

388
00:24:44,547 --> 00:24:45,355
Chien ?

389
00:24:48,218 --> 00:24:49,025
Frère.

390
00:24:54,781 --> 00:24:55,787
Cul sec.

391
00:25:02,823 --> 00:25:03,831
Ton nom ?

392
00:25:06,502 --> 00:25:09,421
